plus_result_nat.content: : forall x y k, nat x -> nat y -> plus x y k -> nat k

fib_square_above.content:
: forall x, nat x ->
    leq (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s z))))))))))))) x ->
    (forall y, times x x y -> (forall u, fib x u -> lt y u))

times_deterministic.content: : forall x y u v, times x y u -> times x y v -> u = v

lt_irreflexive.content: : forall x, nat x -> lt x x -> false

plus_deterministic.content: : forall x y u v, plus x y u -> plus x y v -> u = v

fib_deterministic.content: : forall x y u, fib x y -> fib x u -> y = u

times_result_nat.content: : forall x y k, nat x -> nat y -> times x y k -> nat k

fib_squares.content:
: forall x x2, nat x -> times x x x2 ->
    (fib x x2 -> x = z \/ x = s z \/ x =
       s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s z)))))))))))) /\
    (x = z \/ x = s z \/ x =
       s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s (s z))))))))))) -> fib x x2)
